messages.message:
Hey folks! I just hit AI Hub during a deployment and the page returned with `no healthy upstream`. I don’t know how long it takes to deploy, but long enough for me to ask my wife to check the site on her computer to the same result.

I wonder if there’s something more helpful we could return if a user hits it during a deployment? I know these are probably small time frames, but I can’t say it fostered confidence.
Thanks @jean for the feedback.  This is a very reasonable request.  We'll track it for future releases.  @Varun Jain
